<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<manifest xmlns:android="http://schemas.android.com/apk/res/android" android:versionCode="24" android:versionName="0.9.8.7" package="org.onepf.sample.trivialdrive" platformBuildVersionCode="21" platformBuildVersionName="5.0.1-1624448">
	<uses-sdk android:minSdkVersion="10" android:targetSdkVersion="21" />
	<uses-permission android:name="android.permission.INTERNET" />
	<uses-permission android:name="android.permission.ACCESS_NETWORK_STATE" />
	<uses-permission android:name="org.onepf.openiab.permission.BILLING" />
	<uses-permission android:name="com.android.vending.BILLING" />
	<uses-permission android:name="com.nokia.payment.BILLING" />
	<uses-permission android:name="com.sec.android.iap.permission.BILLING" />
	<uses-feature android:name="android.hardware.telephony" android:required="false" />
	<uses-permission android:name="android.permission.RECEIVE_SMS" />
	<uses-permission android:name="android.permission.SEND_SMS" />
	<uses-permission android:name="android.permission.READ_PHONE_STATE" />
	<uses-permission android:name="com.slideme.sam.manager.inapp.permission.BILLING" />
	<uses-permission android:name="com.skubit.BILLING" />
	<application android:theme="resourceId:0x7f050000" android:label="TrivialDrive" android:icon="res/drawable-ldpi-v4/ic_launcher.png" android:name="org.onepf.sample.trivialdrive.MyApp" android:allowBackup="false">
		<meta-data android:name="iap:api_version" android:value="13" />
		<activity android:label="OPF Trivial Drive" android:name="org.onepf.sample.trivialdrive.MainActivity" android:screenOrientation="portrait" android:configChanges="0x480">
			<intent-filter>
				<action android:name="android.intent.action.MAIN" />
				<category android:name="android.intent.category.LAUNCHER" />
			</intent-filter>
		</activity>
		<receiver android:name="com.amazon.device.iap.ResponseReceiver">
			<intent-filter>
				<action android:name="com.amazon.inapp.purchasing.NOTIFY" android:permission="com.amazon.inapp.purchasing.Permission.NOTIFY" />
			</intent-filter>
		</receiver>
		<receiver android:name="mp.MpSMSReceiver">
			<intent-filter>
				<action android:name="android.provider.Telephony.SMS_RECEIVED" />
			</intent-filter>
		</receiver>
		<service android:name="mp.MpService" />
		<service android:name="mp.StatusUpdateService" />
		<activity android:theme="@android:style/Theme.Translucent.NoTitleBar" android:name="mp.MpActivity" android:configChanges="0x4a0" />
	</application>
